General.Name: Presearch
General.Description: Presearch is an open, decentralized search engine that rewards community members with Presearch Tokens for their usage, contribution to, and promotion of the platform.

ICO.Description:
Primas is an open content release, recommendation and trading ecosphere. The tokens are a utlity token that allow users access to the Primas network. They aim to solve five issues they identify in the content ecosystem.

  1. Solve the credibility of the information overload
  2. To solve the problem of plagiarism and piracy
  3. To solve the problem of the quality of the eye economy brought about by the problem
  4. Address the centralization of the platform to display the content of the intervention
  5. Address privacy and data abuse issues
